[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     11[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     12[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Recipe 12.9 is an exceptional piece of technical writing. The treatment of epidemic forecasting is thorough, technically accurate, and reflects genuine production experience. The multi-source data fusion discussion, the behavioral feedback section, the calibration framework, and the honest take are all outstanding. The architecture is sound, the AWS service selection is well-justified, and the pseudocode is clear and educational. The recipe correctly identifies the ensemble approach as the production standard and references the right institutional frameworks (CDC FluSight, COVID-19 Forecast Hub, CFA, Delphi group).
